These commands can only be run in the directory of project on the local machine. If not,
git clone https://github.com/mrstephenpace/my_projects.git

Status of project
git status

Remove files or folders from the project
git rm -rf name_of_folder
git rm name_of_file


Add a file or folder to project
git add name_of_file

Add all files to project
git add -f -A


Commit the previously added files or folders to the project
git commit -am "comments for commit"

Push commits to the repository
git push origin master
